    # [LCModel.f:14566] C    more than 2*N iterations in the inner loop.  See the DATA statement below.
    # [LCModel.f:14567] C     BASED ON C.L.LAWSON AND R.J.HANSON,
    # [LCModel.f:14568] C     'SOLVING LEAST SQUARES PROBLEMS', PRENTICE-HALL, 1974
